<header>
    <h1>link-preview tester</h1>

    <p>Use this form to test out different combinations of meta tags for enabling previews on social media sites and
        instant messenger apps.</p>
</header>
<form action="/.netlify/functions/link-preview-test">

    <p>Choose which meta tags you'd like to include. You can mix and match.</p>

    {% for item in tagData %}
    <label class="checkbox">
        <input type="checkbox"
               name="{{item.name}}"
               id="{{item.name}}">
        {{item.title}}
        <b aria-hidden="true">âœ”</b>
    </label>
    {% endfor %}

    <p>Use this url to test link previews:</p>
    <div>
        <code id="url">
        </code>
    </div>
    <button class="block noscript-hide">Visit Link Preview Page</button>
</form>